{"tid":4687,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"男泳客愛拿吹風機「烘蛋」　冰島業者苦惱","createTime":"2016-11-26T15:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T20:30:59.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c8f55718f96f81faaf76655ad7f49a62d8e411b","tid":4687,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:07:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/column/article/9/rnews/20160427/847663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Fcolumn%2Farticle%2F9%2Frnews%2F20160427%2F847663&d=XH28pMGT6MRyCCb5fGXV9cW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=a05d105b\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/column/article/9/rnews/20160427/847663</a><br />\n（更新：新增41J配音版影片）<br />\n <br />\n多數的冰島游泳池機構都配有公共吹風機，給民眾一個方便，但有許多泳客在抱怨，常看到男泳客拿著吹風機烘乾下體，讓他們感到噁心與不舒服，也讓冰島的游泳池業者相當苦惱。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，位在首都雷克雅維克的桑德和林游泳池(Sundhollin pool)最近就刊出一份警告海報，海報上明確印著禁止男泳客拿著公共吹風機「烘蛋」，並寫上「這不是陰囊吹風機」，要求泳客不能拿著吹風機吹下體和臀部，還說：「多毛的禿頭老男請自備吹風機，或者是準備吸水力超強的毛巾！」<br />\n <br />\n據悉這個警告規定自去年就開始張貼，並在社交網路間廣為流傳。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"cb18fa28826aed1861462389a0d048cd46f0fdac","tid":4687,"uid":6581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"其實吹下又唔會掂到有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed052173162efe83925d0fde29f16268dbdcc2a","tid":4687,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整部專用好過"},{"pid":"7ccf1d0774bf9d1cbbfea44af2aceea64766c72e","tid":4687,"uid":9291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:12:32.000Z","msg":"施旖婕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc457d56db709b6377d28b92bec2c577b08cdf7d","tid":4687,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"唔吹下有水局住一定好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff999387bc1a50b0791c9edcbe6d7e51c3f1f696","tid":4687,"uid":9586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"袋泥伯"},{"pid":"f58abbc0a2df7427ffd237cd3c4d204fb53bd549","tid":4687,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T20:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}